toolbox.name: Multidimension
toolbox.summary: The Multidimension toolbox contains tools that operate on netCDF data. You can use these tools to make a netCDF raster layer, feature layer, or table view; to convert to netCDF from a raster, feature, or table; and to select a dimension of a netCDF layer or table.

toolset.name: This toolbox does not contain any toolsets
